Usage: report_scan_chain [-help] [-chain <chain_name>] [-out_file <file_name>]
                         [-verbose {true|false}]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-chain <chain_name>                  # name of scan chain (string, optional)
-out_file <file_name>                # scan chain output file
                                     # (string, optional)
-verbose {true|false}                # print out more message (bool, optional)